snippet.title: Pico Racer
snippet.description:
An arcade racing game and a tribute to classic pseudo-3D racers for PICO-8. My first game made for this awesome fantasy console! 

Play in browser: https://kometbomb.itch.io/pico-racer

Game by @kometbomb
